    /**
     * Convert a JSONObject into a well-formed, element-normal XML string.
     *
     * @param object
     *            A JSONObject.
     * @param tagName
     *            The optional name of the enclosing tag.
     * @return A string.
     * @throws JSONException Thrown if there is an error parsing the string
